qas.question: What's the title of Schwarzenegger's autobiography?
What did Schwarzenegger name the chapter of the book that addresses his extramarital affair?

context: Schwarzenegger's autobiography, <a0_0>Total Recall<a0_0/>, was released in <a2_0>October 2012<a2_0/>. He devotes one chapter called <a1_0>"The Secret"<a1_0/> to his extramarital affair. The majority of his book is about his successes in the three major chapters in his life: bodybuilder, actor, and Governor of California.
